title: [Cleric Guild, Courtyard]
description: A limestone walkway crosses briefly with a tiny rivulet as it winds its way towards a mist-shrouded stone temple.  Rows of slender limbed trees nearly obscure the high seashell-inset walls that enclose this courtyard.  As the sea breeze propels the leafy foliage into motion, a shady bower reveals a darkened tunnel leading into the earth.
